{"tid":1379183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遇惡犬裝備升級討論","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T18:02:23.000Z","uid":129988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7d22ea979e0cf5865a19fe96643b700fe6dbaccc","tid":1379183,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:57:32.000Z","msg":"呢排周街好多惡犬<br />\n尤其入黑特別多<br />\n香港市民理應多啲保護自己<br />\n除咗一般裝備以外<br />\n有以下推介<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">麻繩</span><br />\n呢排見到有一班人俾大量狗突然發狗癲就俾狗咬<br />\n其實咁突然一定會甩一兩件<br />\n如果有繩可以試下set條終點線俾佢<br />\n但記住狗就冇人咁高<br />\n就set低啲<br />\n當然小心有人行嘅時候佢地會仆低<br />\n到時要大嗌<br />\n睇撚住呀！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">潤滑劑or油or鹼液</span><br />\n都係上面個問題啦<br />\n最近見到啲暴徒用滅火桶搞到地下咁滑<br />\n搞到差人叔叔做唔到野！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都令我諗到點對付惡犬<br />\n用鹼液加搵下有冇啲大水源<br />\n洗下地<br />\n等啲狗仔沖下泡泡浴溜下冰<br />\n唔會咬你<br />\n咁但係油性嘅會唔會起火就唔知喇<br />\n大家唔好食煙整到自己<br />\n有代替品就唔好用喇<br />\n<br />\n至於 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">火</span> 呢<br />\n就一定唔可以用！<br />\n啲人話差人叔叔驚火<br />\n啲衰狗又點會唔驚呢<br />\n我重申<br />\n差人叔叔天不怕地不怕<br />\n佢地只係見到火就按程序俾消防叔叔處理返先姐<br />\n所以切勿 係切勿 用火！<br />\n咁係幫 唔 到你爭取時間走架！<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩法寶，大家可以旁下身？"},{"pid":"38ba2deb2633353f9d1c1bbf75629c375318c72d","tid":1379183,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def31f54070879aa520d317160636a3d9dbdf1ba","tid":1379183,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:59:24.000Z","msg":"有冇養狗嘅朋友講下點阻止俾狗咬"},{"pid":"be630cb4d6b7cd13d908b607ca86acefdc1813e9","tid":1379183,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:00:07.000Z","msg":"最近先知香港咁多狗"},{"pid":"e733d4c59334661f6e525daa7b446929b674bdcf","tid":1379183,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d577e7bf35088abb31f91425f0c3af1181af33f","tid":1379183,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:00:43.000Z","msg":"堆"},{"pid":"e3198000732c0f73af8bd524f3ebf9ab424b1d2e","tid":1379183,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:00:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20aec6e04caddccabe890f94a4dee66f0d759a79","tid":1379183,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:01:17.000Z","msg":"唔怪自冇人應，應該開寵物台？"},{"pid":"ff36ebc17f8d2d7fab66a0f61d3bbd4e5a90f9a6","tid":1379183,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}